\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0                 NEW FEATURE: FACTION LIST}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0       }
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0        * This is a new feature for playing World of Warcraft that allows players to mark all of their available faction slots on their action bars for quick and easy access. This will help players who have limited time or resources to dedicate to all ten supported factions.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0        * To access the new FACTION LIST, players must select a faction from the list in the UI, then click the "Faction" tab at the bottom of the list. From there, players can mark all of the available faction slots for a zone, allowing them to quickly and easily group with other players of the same faction.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0        * FACTION GUILDS are now available. Players may join as many as three factions from a single action bar. Players may be in a group for a given faction at a time, but only on a limited number of actions.}
